.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL_PENDING_HTLCS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-pending-htlcs \- list channels with pending HTLCs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-pending-htlcs
.RI [ channel_id ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns channels that have one or more in-flight HTLCs.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
